    from marketingFeedBaseTable
    ) a
group by pogMarketingFeedBaseTab
","temp.pogs_nmso")

run(sql="
select distinct a.pogId, 
                count(distinct case when lower(b.Channel) like '%fb%' then b.subOrderId end)/7 as FB_ADS
FROM `temp.disablePogs` a 
left join (
            select distinct b.pogId, 
                            a.subOrderId, 
                            a.orderDate, 
                            a.Channel 
            from `temp.order_sd` a 
            left join `all(agCmDump)` b 
            on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
            WHERE DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),a.orderDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 7
            ) b 
on a.pogId=b.pogId
group by a.pogId
order by FB_ADS desc
limit 50
",1000)

run(sql="
select distinct a.pogId,
                count(distinct case when lower(b.Channel) like '%fb%' and lower(b.utmContent) like '%cpt%' then b.subOrderId end)/7 as FB_CPT_ADS,
                c.NM3SO
FROM `temp.appendPogs` a 
left join (
            select distinct b.pogId, 
                            a.subOrderId, 
                            a.orderDate, 
                            a.Channel,
                            a.utmContent
            from `temp.order_sd` a 
            left join `all(agCmDump)` b 
            on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
            WHERE DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),a.orderDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 7
            ) b 
on a.pogId=b.pogId
left join `temp.pogs_nmso` c on a.pogId=c.pogId
group by a.pogId, c.NM3SO
order by FB_CPT_ADS desc
limit 50
",1000)
